OL,3,C'We need to do better': Council
OL,4,Capology after mowing down newly
OL,5,Cplanted bulbs
OL,7,FBristol City Council has apologised to
OL,8,Fa community group after mowing down
OL,9,F30,000 bulbs in a park just days after
OL,10,Fthey were planted.
OL,12,FThe Friends of St George Park raised
OL,13,F#6,000 to fund the project they had
OL,14,Fbeen advised by the council what to
OL,15,Fplant and where, and two councillors
OL,16,Fhad helped with the planting.
OL,18,FJust days later the council mowed the
OL,19,Farea over, destroying all their bulbs.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
