PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1773914712
OL,3,C'We need to do better': Council
OL,4,Capology after mowing down newly
OL,5,Cplanted bulbs
OL,7,FNow in an apology to the volunteers
OL,8,Fand the winder community the council
OL,9,Fhas said it needs to 'do better'.
OL,11,FCouncillor Heather Mack, Deputy Leader
OL,12,Fof Bristol City Council, said: "All of
OL,13,Fthe hard work that the local
OL,14,Fvolunteers and community put into
OL,15,Fimproving the local area and making it
OL,16,Fmore enjoyable for everyone visiting
OL,17,FSt George Park is hugely valued and
OL,18,Fappreciated.
OL,20,F"We are incredibly sorry for this
OL,21,Fmistake - it should not have happened.
OL,26,@tD@`OU|D@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
