PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1773914712
OL,3,C'We need to do better': Council
OL,4,Capology after mowing down newly
OL,5,Cplanted bulbs
OL,7,F"We will ensure Friends of St George
OL,8,FPark receive payment to cover the cost
OL,9,Fof the bulbs that they worked so hard
OL,10,Fto raise money for, and help the
OL,11,Fcommunity with any events to plant new
OL,12,Fbulbs, as well as support upcoming
OL,13,Fcommunity led activities to improve
OL,14,Fthe local park area.
OL,16,F"We know that communicating with and
OL,17,Fsharing information between officers
OL,18,Fworking in our parks needs to be
OL,19,Fbetter.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
