CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1773914712
OL,3,C'We need to do better': Council
OL,4,Capology after mowing down newly
OL,5,Cplanted bulbs
OL,7,F"The parks service is in the process
OL,8,Fof moving to an online system for
OL,9,Fallocating work to our grounds
OL,10,Fmaintenance teams.
OL,12,F"This new system will give teams
OL,13,Faccess to real time information, via
OL,14,Fphones and tablets, on work and
OL,15,Fprojects completed by staff and
OL,16,Fvolunteers as well as changes to
OL,17,Fmaintenance needs.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
